{"tid":1875648,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國郵政停收寄中港澳郵件","createTime":"2020-02-12T02:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T02:28:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eecfd933cfbde14ecf2b1d9222aab59facf08062","tid":1875648,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:06:39.000Z","msg":"美國郵政署宣布，即時停收寄往中國、香港以及澳門的郵件及包裹，因為航空公司相繼暫停到中港澳航班，派送郵件及包裹遇上極大困難，停收郵件措施會直到運輸能力回復為止。美國主要快遞公司由於有各自貨運機隊，寄往中國的快遞服務暫時未受影響。<br />\n<br />\n中國郵政則表示，正逐步為郵政局、郵件處理中心和郵車消毒，確保新冠肺炎病毒不會經郵件傳播，強調病毒在物品表面生存時間不長，接收來自中國的郵件沒有風險，而寄到中國的郵件不會以面對面方式派送。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1263235&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1263235%26csid%3D261_367&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BYjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=4559ceb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1263235&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"ca8ef1f3333afa3929e507af743c4926cdf74bd1","tid":1875648,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:28:24.000Z","msg":"咁我amazon訂啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}